Content

This repository is structured as follow:

  • data/: contains a sampled of data used in the article. The folder is split in two folders: data/raw/ to find a sample of all raw data (acoustic, eddy trajectories, chloro and sst) ; and data/intermediate/ with some intermediate .Rdata files, to make easily the Figures.

  • figures/: contains the figures used to validate et visualize the outputs.

  • scripts/: contains R scripts to run the workflow. The order to run these scripts is explained in each name of files and follow the Workflow description.
